channel.title: Run.bat help
channel.description:
what do i put in the runserver.bat because now when i run it it tells me The system cannot find the path specified. Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: Jframe Caused by: java.lang.ClassNotFoundException: Jframe at java.net.URLClassLoader$1.run(Unknown Source) at java.security.AccessController.doPrivileged(Native Method) at java.net.URLClassLoader.findClass(Unknown Source) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(Unknown Source) at sun.misc.Launcher$AppClassLoader.loadClass(Unknown Source) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(Unknown Source) Could not find the main class: Jframe. Program will exit. Press any key to continue . . .
and i put in there when i edited it @echo off title SMitedscape cd Smitedscape java -Xmx300m Jframe 10 0 highmem members 32 pause ( the source is exion)
